It is possible to conceive a scenario where 3 different BWPs are configured as shown in FIG. 1B, each having same or different center frequency, different (band-) width and/or different subcarrier spacing:
BWP1 with a width of 40 MHz and subcarrier spacing of 15 kHz;
BWP2 with a width of 10 MHz and subcarrier spacing of 15 kHz;
